<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 04:08:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国国会通过避免政府关门的法案，并将其发送给乔·拜登</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-congress-passes-bill-to-avert-government-shutdown-sends-it-to-biden/articleshow/106973785.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106973785.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国众议院通过了一项权宜之计法案，为联邦政府提供资金直至三月初，避免了政府关门。参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默宣布了这一好消息，而一些极右翼众议院共和党人则表示反对。该法案将上一财年的支出水平延长至3月1日和3月8日，为全年预算采取行动提供了更多时间。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-congress-passes-bill-to-avert-government-shutdown-sends-it-to-biden/articleshow/106973785.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国称胡塞武装向油轮发射导弹但未造成任何损害</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-says-iran-backed-houthis-launched-missiles-at-tanker-ship-but-no-damage-caused/articleshow/106972975.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106972975.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据美国海军称，伊朗支持的胡塞民兵周四晚间向一艘美国油轮发射了两枚反舰弹道导弹，击中附近海域，但没有造成人员伤亡或财产损失。控制也门大部分地区的胡塞武装很早就声称对此次袭击负责，称他们使用海军导弹瞄准“化学游骑兵”号舰艇，导致“直接命中”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:07:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-says-iran-backed-houthis-launched-missiles-at-tanker-ship-but-no-damage-caused/articleshow/106972975.cms</guid></item><item><title>苏纳克在政党对卢旺达政策的反抗中幸存下来</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/sunak-survives-party-rebellion-on-rwanda-policy/articleshow/106973305.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106973305.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/sunak-survives-party-rebellion-on-rwanda-policy/articleshow/106973305.cms</guid></item><item><title>谢丽尔·桑德伯格 (Sheryl Sandberg) 退出 Meta 董事会 12 年后</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/sheryl-sandberg-to-exit-meta-board-after-12-years/articleshow/106973060.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106973060.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Meta Platforms 前首席运营官谢丽尔·桑德伯格 (Sheryl Sandberg) 周三在 Facebook 上表示，她计划在 5 月份任期结束后辞去公司董事会职务。桑德伯格在帖子中表示：“元业务很强大，并且为未来做好了准备，所以现在感觉是离开的最佳时机。”她补充说，她将担任该公司的顾问。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/sheryl-sandberg-to-exit-meta-board-after-12-years/articleshow/106973060.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度对巴基斯坦报复伊朗保持沉默</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/india-silent-on-pakistans-retaliatory-strikes-on-iran/articleshow/106973615.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106973615.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度在对伊朗空袭表示理解后，没有就巴基斯坦与伊朗问题发表评论。印度认为，伊朗的行动证明了其在跨境恐怖主义问题上的立场。总部位于巴基斯坦的恐怖组织“Jaish al Adl”成为伊朗的攻击目标。巴基斯坦当局不愿对恐怖组织采取行动，这阻碍了与印度的双边接触。 “我们发布了一份新闻稿，明确了我们对恐怖主义的立场。我们不会对巴基斯坦和伊朗问题发表评论，”MEA 发言人表示。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:20:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/india-silent-on-pakistans-retaliatory-strikes-on-iran/articleshow/106973615.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的儿子称塔克·卡尔森担任美国副总统“在谈判桌上”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-son-suggests-tucker-carlson-as-potential-vice-presidential-running-mate/articleshow/106972128.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106972128.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;小特朗普在接受有线频道Newsmax谈论他是否会考虑卡尔森时表示，这个选择“已经摆在桌面上”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-son-suggests-tucker-carlson-as-potential-vice-presidential-running-mate/articleshow/106972128.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国一周内第四次袭击目标胡塞武装</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/in-4th-hit-in-a-week-us-targets-houthis/articleshow/106973580.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106973580.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国袭击也门胡塞武装军事基地，伊朗支持的民兵继续袭击商船和海军军舰。袭击摧毁了胡塞武装控制地区的导弹和发射器。美国采取行动保护国际海员和商业航线。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/in-4th-hit-in-a-week-us-targets-houthis/articleshow/106973580.cms</guid></item><item><title>国会批准拨款以避免美国政府关门</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/congress-approves-funding-us-government-shutdown-temporary-spending-bill-partial-us-government-shutdown-white-house/articleshow/106971914.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971914.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;国会通过了一项临时支出法案，以避免美国政府本周末部分关闭，并将该法案提交给白宫。乔·拜登总统计划签署该协议。短期资金将在 3 月 1 日之前为美国机构提供资金，在 3 月 8 日之前为其他机构提供资金。众议院共和党人投票反对该措施，而民主党人则支持该措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:52:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/congress-approves-funding-us-government-shutdown-temporary-spending-bill-partial-us-government-shutdown-white-house/articleshow/106971914.cms</guid></item><item><title>“中国专家在正式通知世界前两周绘制了新冠病毒图谱”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-experts-mapped-covid-virus-2-weeks-before-officially-informing-world/articleshow/106971379.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971379.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据媒体报道，中国研究人员团队至少在中国正式向世界通报该病毒两周前，就发现并绘制了导致 Covid-19 大流行的 SARS-CoV-2 病毒。这些报告基于美国卫生与公众服务部（HHS）的文件，并与美国国会委员会共享，引发了人们对中国在病毒问题上的透明度的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-experts-mapped-covid-virus-2-weeks-before-officially-informing-world/articleshow/106971379.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本“月球狙击手”航天器尝试历史性登月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/japans-moon-sniper-spacecraft-attempts-historic-lunar-landing/articleshow/106971824.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971824.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本的“月球狙击手”航天器正准备在周六午夜进行历史性的月球着陆，该国希望利用精确技术在许多失败的领域取得成功。凭借其月球勘察智能着陆器（SLIM）任务，日本希望成为第五个在月球岩石表面实现极其棘手的软着陆的国家。迄今为止，只有美国、苏联、中国和印度完成了这一壮举。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/japans-moon-sniper-spacecraft-attempts-historic-lunar-landing/articleshow/106971824.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜进行水下核武器系统测试</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/n-korea-says-tested-underwater-nuclear-weapon-system-after-trilateral-drills/articleshow/106971800.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971800.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜周五表示，它已经测试了“水下核武器系统”，以回应华盛顿、首尔和东京的联合海军演习，其中有一艘美国核动力航空母舰参与。一份声明称，这些演习“严重威胁朝鲜的安全”，因此作为回应，平壤“在朝鲜东海对其正在开发的水下核武器系统‘Haeil-5-23’进行了一次重要测试”。国家通讯社朝中社报道的国防部消息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/n-korea-says-tested-underwater-nuclear-weapon-system-after-trilateral-drills/articleshow/106971800.cms</guid></item><item><title>红海袭击：全球航运陷入困境，美国再次袭击胡塞武装目标</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/red-sea-attacks-us-strikes-houthi-targets-as-global-shipping-faces-threat/articleshow/106971766.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971766.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国军方对也门胡塞叛军军事基地进行第五次打击，目标是被视为对海上交通“迫在眉睫的威胁”的导弹。美国运营的 Genco Picardy 号船只在亚丁湾遭到袭击。美国的立场强调针对胡塞武装的侵略性导弹袭击的自卫。对关键全球贸易路线的攻击会导致路线改变并影响供应链。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:39:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/red-sea-attacks-us-strikes-houthi-targets-as-global-shipping-faces-threat/articleshow/106971766.cms</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝美国推动巴勒斯坦建国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/netanyahu-defies-us-calls-for-de-escalation-vows-continued-offensive-in-gaza/articleshow/106971400.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971400.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列总理内塔尼亚胡驳回了美国关于缓和以色列在加沙地带军事行动并建立巴勒斯坦国的呼吁；白宫谴责内塔尼亚胡。内塔尼亚胡发誓将继续军事努力，直到哈马斯被解散并释放人质。美国呼吁建立巴勒斯坦国和两国解决方案，而内塔尼亚胡以安全问题为由表示反对。白宫国家安全发言人约翰·柯比承认存在不同的观点，并表示：“我们显然有不同的看法。”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/netanyahu-defies-us-calls-for-de-escalation-vows-continued-offensive-in-gaza/articleshow/106971400.cms</guid></item><item><title>《奥本海默》以 13 比 5 项提名击败《芭比娃娃》获得英国电影学院奖提名</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/oppenheimer-tops-bafta-nominations-with-13-nods/articleshow/106971321.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106971321.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周四，历史剧《奥本海默》在英国电影学院奖提名中领跑，获得 13 项提名。充满性色彩的哥特式喜剧《Poor Things》获得 11 项提名，马丁·斯科塞斯 (Martin Scorsese) 的《花月杀手》讲述 1920 年代奥色治族成员被谋杀的故事，获得 9 项提名。这三部电影将与法庭剧《跌倒的解剖》和《守望者》一起角逐颁奖典礼的最高奖项——最佳影片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/oppenheimer-tops-bafta-nominations-with-13-nods/articleshow/106971321.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登称巴基斯坦的袭击表明伊朗在该地区并不“受欢迎”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/biden-pakistan-and-iran-strikes-reveal-irans-unpopularity-in-the-region/articleshow/106966729.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106966729.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登周四表示，巴基斯坦和伊朗对彼此领土的空袭表明，在日益紧张的地区，德黑兰并不“受欢迎”。拜登在白宫对记者说：“正如你所看到的，伊朗在该地区并不是特别受欢迎。”他补充说，“我们正在努力”了解局势将如何发展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:41:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/biden-pakistan-and-iran-strikes-reveal-irans-unpopularity-in-the-region/articleshow/106966729.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国官员：鉴于俄罗斯的合作，朝鲜威胁可能会“彻底”改变</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-threat-and-russia-cooperation-us-official-warns-of-drastic-changes/articleshow/106966579.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106966579.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:30:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-threat-and-russia-cooperation-us-official-warns-of-drastic-changes/articleshow/106966579.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本签署购买 400 枚战斧导弹的协议，美国特使赞扬其国防建设</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-signs-agreement-to-purchase-400-tomahawk-missiles-as-us-envoy-lauds-its-defense-buildup/articleshow/106965894.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106965894.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:34:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-signs-agreement-to-purchase-400-tomahawk-missiles-as-us-envoy-lauds-its-defense-buildup/articleshow/106965894.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普手上神秘红痕背后隐藏着什么</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/whats-behind-mysterious-red-marks-on-trumps-hands/articleshow/106963219.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106963219.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普在前往让·卡罗尔受审期间留下的红色痕迹引发了猜测。 Joshua Zeichner 博士讨论了潜在的原因，包括干燥、体力活动引起的水泡、酸橙汁反应和其他原因。特朗普在无视警告并发表评论后面临被逐出审判。法官刘易斯·A.</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 13:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/whats-behind-mysterious-red-marks-on-trumps-hands/articleshow/106963219.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾剩余的太平洋盟友承诺支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-remaining-pacific-allies-pledge-support/articleshow/106945944.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106945944.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;瑙鲁在总统选举几天后决定断交，台湾剩下的太平洋岛国盟友也表示支持，台湾在该地区的外交足迹减少到三个国家。尽管中美在安全关系以及提供基础设施和融资方面的竞争加剧，但随着瑙鲁的离开，台湾的地区盟友自 2019 年以来已从 6 个减少到 3 个。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 04:49:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-remaining-pacific-allies-pledge-support/articleshow/106945944.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国和菲律宾寻求更好的沟通和管理南海冲突</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-philippines-seek-better-communication-management-of-conflicts-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/106945162.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106945162.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中菲同意通过友好对话改善海上沟通、化解矛盾。他们重申，南海争端并不是双边关系的全部。双方同意冷静处理事件，妥善处理包括仁爱礁局势在内的海上突发事件。双方还推​​进海上务实合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 04:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-philippines-seek-better-communication-management-of-conflicts-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/106945162.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>